WEBVTT

00:00.759 --> 00:01.626
He's an observer.

00:01.627 --> 00:03.177
They only show up
at significant events.

00:03.244 --> 00:04.478
That he's here
must mean it's important.

00:04.564 --> 00:05.999
Previously on <i>Fringe...</i>

00:06.066 --> 00:08.077
<i>He wants to go into</i>
<i>the observer's mind.</i>

00:08.080 --> 00:09.047
I do not have long.

00:09.114 --> 00:12.300
I need you
to do something for me.

00:12.856 --> 00:14.941
Walter.

00:15.433 --> 00:17.601
How can she have memories
of my Olivia's life

00:17.668 --> 00:19.019
that are clearer to her
than her own?

00:19.104 --> 00:21.055
No matter how badly
I want my Olivia back,

00:21.139 --> 00:23.524
I can't make this one have
memories she didn't experience.

00:23.608 --> 00:25.642
I think you are.
Even without meaning to.

00:25.694 --> 00:26.944
And it's wrong, Peter.

00:27.011 --> 00:28.862
I don't understand
what's happening to me,

00:28.947 --> 00:31.115
but if you look into my eyes,
you can see that I am her.

00:31.182 --> 00:32.849
No.
I know she's out there--

00:32.901 --> 00:35.953
my Olivia in my timeline.
I'm sorry.

00:36.020 --> 00:38.906
I think it's better
if I just stay away.

